"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?7/24/7557/abstract/26\">",
"      Soriano-Sarabia N, Abad MA, Vallejo A, et al. Influence of hepatitis C and hepatitis G virus co-infection on viral and cellular dynamics in patients infected with human immunodeficiency virus following interruption of highly active anti-retroviral therapy. Clin Microbiol Infect 2006; 12:290.",
"     </a>",
